{"_path":"/councilor/service/s2024","_dir":"service","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"龜山建設大願景，公園道路優先行！","description":null,"image":"/images/service/s2024-1.jpeg","sequence":2024,"category1":"A. 健全都市發展","category2":"A.1 加速宜居城市建設","link":"https://www.facebook.com/groups/a7xinlinkou/permalink/706404014798183/","author":"李宗豪","head":{"meta":[{"name":"keywords","content":""},{"name":"robots","content":""},{"name":"author","content":"李宗豪"},{"name":"copyright","content":"© 2024 A7新林口-社區網站"},{"name":"og:title","content":"地方行政"}]},"publishedAt":"2024-04-25T00:00:00.000Z","toc":true,"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"龜山建設大願景公園道路優先行"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"龜山建設大願景，公園道路優先行！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"本週質詢工務局、水務局、教育局，先來報告幾項建設進度。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"▪️ 新闢道路"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n1、青山路連接振興路"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n這條路在我一上任就積極找工務局討論，爭取重新評估，工務局也有找到突破工法，讓這條路死灰復燃。\n用地取得作業已經完成，目前正在進行細部設計，有機會在今年底發包施工，未來可以紓解 A7 文青路到文化一路的塞車問題。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n2、變一道路"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nT 字變一字，高架改地下，期程要再延，經費要上漲，去年承諾「工期縮短、減少經費」直接跳票！\n局長說，為了工程穩定性，維護文資設施，需要再拖一年，明年才有機會開工。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"▪️ 公園規劃"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n1、A7 滯洪池公園（公滯 1）"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n預計會在今年 7 月開工，先進行濕轉乾工程，明年規劃設計變成公園！"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n2、大坪頂公園（公九）"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n用地取得已召開第一次公聽會，與地主取得初步共識，速度將會比文高三快，未來有機會變成大型旗艦公園。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"這幾案我會持續追蹤，下集報告學校建設篇。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"s2024-1.jpeg","src":"/images/service/s2024-1.jpeg"},"children":[]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"龜山建設大願景公園道路優先行","depth":2,"text":"龜山建設大願景，公園道路優先行！"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:councilor:service:s2024.md","_source":"content","_file":"councilor/service/s2024.md","_extension":"md"}